00:11:22,541 --> 00:11:24,791
But in these times,
we cannot sit and wait!

249
00:11:24,875 --> 00:11:26,208
We must find those good things

250
00:11:26,291 --> 00:11:28,625
even if we have to dig up
every inch of this Earth!

251
00:11:28,708 --> 00:11:30,500
So then, let's go
search for them!

252
00:11:30,583 --> 00:11:31,375
For what?

253
00:11:31,458 --> 00:11:33,541
The mysteries of this world!

254
00:11:33,625 --> 00:11:36,166
[KYON] And with that, we are now
going on a tour around the city

255
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:38,500
in search of mystery
and phenomena.

256
00:11:38,583 --> 00:11:41,583
On Saturday, meet at 9 am in
front of Kitaguchi Station.

257
00:11:41,666 --> 00:11:44,166
Those who arrive late shall
receive the death penalty.

258
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:45,958
Death penalty...?

259
00:11:46,041 --> 00:11:49,958
You know, I really hate
to waste a day off...

260
00:11:50,041 --> 00:11:52,333
You're late! Penalty!

261
00:11:52,416 --> 00:11:55,541
[KYON] Haruhi's proposal:
Split off into groups of two,

262
00:11:55,625 --> 00:11:57,625
search the city for
mysterious phenomena.

263
00:11:57,708 --> 00:12:00,000
If we find any, alert
the others via cell phone.

264
00:12:00,083 --> 00:12:01,083
That is all.

265
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:04,750
I guess we got our groups.

266
00:12:04,833 --> 00:12:07,083
[KYON] It might be a lucky
day for me after all.

267
00:12:07,166 --> 00:12:09,833
I mean, if I can go on
a date with Miss Asahina,

268
00:12:09,916 --> 00:12:11,416
treating everyone to lunch
