only place to do it.

412
00:17:49,166 --> 00:17:50,958
[KYON]
Oh brother.

413
00:17:56,708 --> 00:17:58,125
[screams]

414
00:17:59,625 --> 00:18:01,750
[HARUHI] What time do you
think it is you idiot?!

415
00:18:01,833 --> 00:18:03,791
[KYON] Sorry, but I
actually just woke up.

416
00:18:03,875 --> 00:18:04,666
[HARUHI]
Huh?!

417
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:07,208
What did you just say to me?!

418
00:18:07,291 --> 00:18:08,791
We were supposed to meet
you at four, right?

419
00:18:08,875 --> 00:18:12,125
[HARUHI] Get your butt back
here! You got 30 seconds!

420
00:18:12,208 --> 00:18:13,583
[KYON]
I had my work cut out for me.

421
00:18:13,666 --> 00:18:14,833
We had to leave,

