442
00:18:59,416 --> 00:19:02,833
[KYON]
And with that, she stormed off.

443
00:19:02,916 --> 00:19:04,333
[sighs]

444
00:19:06,125 --> 00:19:07,916
[KYON]
You're kidding me...

