00:19:17,833 --> 00:19:19,000
You're on your own there.

450
00:19:19,083 --> 00:19:20,250
[sighs]

451
00:19:20,333 --> 00:19:22,041
Hey, Suzumiya, ever happen
to hear the story

452
00:19:22,125 --> 00:19:23,708
