of happiness?

453
00:19:23,791 --> 00:19:25,541
What about it?

454
00:19:25,625 --> 00:19:28,083
Nevermind, it doesn't have
to do with anything.

455
00:19:28,166 --> 00:19:30,041
Then don't talk about it.

456
00:19:30,125 --> 00:19:32,791
[KYON] After being showered from
behind by Haruhi's aura of

457
00:19:32,875 --> 00:19:36,750
