00:19:45,416 --> 00:19:47,875
talk to me about
regarding Suzumiya?

462
00:19:47,958 --> 00:19:49,166
Heh...

463
00:19:50,708 --> 00:19:52,625
[KOIZUMI] I get the feeling that
the other two have already

