474
00:20:12,958 --> 00:20:15,416
To tell you the truth, I wasn't
planning on transferring

475
00:20:15,500 --> 00:20:16,833
into this school so suddenly,

476
00:20:16,916 --> 00:20:18,583
but the circumstances
have changed.

477
00:20:18,666 --> 00:20:20,500
And I have to say that
I really didn't expect

478
00:20:20,583 --> 00:20:24,083
the two of them to join up with
Haruhi Suzumiya so quickly.

479
00:20:24,166 --> 00:20:26,583
Either way, I'm sure we're going
to have the chance to talk more

480
00:20:26,666 --> 00:20:29,375
