something to show you.

482
00:20:32,291 --> 00:20:34,791
But for now, I think I'll give
you the short version.

483
00:20:34,875 --> 00:20:36,625
The organization that
I belong to has

484
00:20:36,708 --> 00:20:39,833
other ESPers besides yours
