487
00:20:43,125 --> 00:20:45,416
And ever since the organization
started up three years ago,

488
00:20:45,500 --> 00:20:47,666
we've been watching
over Miss Suzumiya.

489
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:49,000
Three years ago.

490
00:20:49,083 --> 00:20:52,083
